title: Handi Bot
description:
Soar through the skies in a world ruled by bots. Use your hook to swing from building to building and travel the farthest distance possible in this skill based action game. Timing and reaction will determine whether you stick your landing or fall to the ground. It's easy to begin your journey but with each Meter you travel, it will become increasingly more difficult!


Challenge your friends to beat your score through Google Play Games!

- Simple one tap input
- Tap towards the sky at an angle to launch your hook
- Tap again while in the air to detach your hook and land
- Travel as for as you can while the difficulty increases over time


Handi Bot was created with an unfortunate handicap when the factory which crafted him had a malfunction on the production line. Born with one hand, Handi Bot wasn't able to fulfill his purpose of taking over the human race along with the other bots, rendering him an outcast among the machines. Fortunately, after several years of ridicule had passed, Handi Bot received news that a factory recall was replacing all malfunctioning bots with more advanced equipment suitable for traversing the terrain of the humans. Now, bearing a hook launcher instead of a hand, Handi Bot is able to soar past his peers and is revered as a hero, icon, and legend in the robot world.

title: SphereKnight
description:
In the heat of the battle his body turns into a ball.
Control SphereKnight with the flick of your finger for some fresh, exciting and tense rolling action! 



This is an auto-save game.
Do not close the application during saving!
Doing so may corrupt the save file.



In the heat of the battle his body turns into a ball.
The one that possesses these mysterious powers is known as the Cosmos Apostle, and it is he who must stop the incoming invasion of chaos.

The ruined kingdom of Lebralia

Those who dare enter this forbidden land are haunted by a ‘cursed mask’.
SphereKnight now steps foot on this land ready to take on his mission as the Cosmos Apostle. 



•Experience a new type of action game in which you swipe the screen to control the ball shaped knight. 
•Feel the thrill of excitement when you defeat many enemies with just one rolling dash attack!
•Feel the satisfaction of mastering the use of the Auras created when SphereKnight uses his dash attacks!



•Items you pick up along your adventure can be upgraded in the magic shop.
•Collect enough materials on your adventure to be able to forge new armour and magical swords.
•Magical swords are an intrinsic part of this game.  Each one has their own aura type created when you dash attack so making use of them well will help greatly expand your play strategy.



•A total of 33 stages and eight fearsome boss battles await you. 
•An additional endless stage run feature is also included. 
•The cursed mask that hauntingly follows SphereKnight calls forth evil creatures to attack.  Depending on SphereKnight’s actions, newer and even stronger enemies will appear.

title: World War Counter Shooter - Battle Royale Survival
description:
Highways games would like to welcome you to our new World War Counter Shooter - Battle Royale Survival game. This is not simple shooting arena game however it is an action-packed shooting game. As the leader of the rebellion, you will face the army of the enemy corp: elite soldiers, lethal special units, mechs with impenetrable shields, powerful tanks… Take the control of the battlefield, deal with the conflict as a real war machine. Become the legend of this world war in the most addictive fps multiplayer.	
Actually hostile army frontiers attacked on your country and you were short of weapons and cover bases. At the time of attack, few teams of yours militants were not present in army bases and they were on training of Frontline Fury at mountain areas. There was no backup of defending the country and enemy army just attacked, they destroyed agency bases and other army squads. Now they have killed all of your companions and its last day battleground. You’ve to save your futuristic city.
Its last man survival with gangster strike missions. Let’s take the road to defeat the enemy’s wave for WW2 survival. Player will freely roam in the arena; just hold the shooting gun accurately at pointed position & shoot the competitors down. Go and search the strike weapons for your battle survival. Use the various army sniper weapons and item to abolish the adversary.
If you’re looking for war of commando and modern counter then here’s a great chance for you to become the expert shooter of ultimate battle royal. Get excited because we’ve implemented auto run controls and battle props just like army bases. You can also get hide behind the props, destroy the enemy shooting helicopters and become US army sniper.
This anti-crime is full of action and thrill shooting in the heroic war of commando. Being a shooter of the modern counter, you know how to fight in the battleground. So it’s a time to stance in the war for ultimate battle royale. So indulge yourself in the shooting assignment of critical craft against your foe.
Feel the new experience unique in shooter games. Press the screen, pull the trigger and shoot! Destroy and annihilate all the bad guys with your powerful weapons and your well-assembled team of heroes!

title: Tank Battle Heroes: World of Shooting
description:
Hey Tank Commander, the real MULTIPLAYER TANK BATTLE GAME is finally AVAILABLE for your mobile! 

Get ready for the tank warfare and jump into the war action in modern PvP tank shooter! Choose your tank, upgrade your deadly weapon and get ready for real World War in an exciting arena where there's danger around every corner! Destroy enemies, aim precisely, shoot fast and dominate the world full of different tanks!

 FEATURES: 
- Choose the best strategy and make right decisions! 
- Feel the spirit of real tank battlefields!
- Unlock and upgrade your war machines!
- Choose between various war machines categories from WW2 classics to modern ones!
- Defend your country or break frontlines with no mercy!
- Conquer every battlefield and fight against players from United States, Japan, Russia, Germany, and more!
- Become a hero driving your tank through European battlefields!

 ENDLESS TANK BATTLES! 
Enjoy endless gameplay with different enemies! It means a different kind of weapon you must choose. Every single available tank will act differently on the battleground. Experience real clash of tank gunners and play against your battle rivals! Achieve victory, test the full power of each tank and increase its field of gunfire – powerful armory awaits! Have you ever imagined taking part in tank team battles?

 BECOME A LEGEND ON THE BATTLEGROUND! 
Hey Soldier, make your way in the history of modern battlegrounds! Crash the enemy, move forward to the victory and put your name in the online hall of fame! Imagine the World of WW2! Show what you are made of and conquer every battleground. There is only one proper tank warfare strategy – begin now!

 3 UNIQUE TANK BATTLEFIELDS! 
Do you want to prove your worth? Test your skills in various tank world conditions and strike for victory through different battlegrounds! Defeat the enemy on the ice, desert and deep in the forest. Every map requires a different pack of skills - we count on you! Prepare yourself and keep an eye right on the enemy! Fight and shoot your enemies in various WWII battlefields. Become a tank battle hero!

 DIFFERENT IRON WARFARE SETTINGS! 
Make your way to the victory in every available tank and unlock all the options to customize your war machine's weapon! Conquer the world on every possible map and find yourself in different conditions. Expect tough fights and clever enemies. Experience real clash of tank commanders destroying your opponents in fast-paced real-time tank combat.

 ONLINE MULTIPLAYER BATTLES! 
Time to see in action the most powerful tanks, modern battlefield! Tank Battle is a free tanks game with astonishing surroundings with outstanding 3D graphics! Hey Soldier, keep an eye on every detail of your weapon and enemy's armor! Don't forget to watch your back - rivals are waiting for your mistake! Join armored warfare now!

 Download this totally new fast-paced shooting game with tanks!

title: All-Star Troopers
description:
Time to lead the ultimate battle through space in the new action-packed strategy builder, All-Star Troopers!

Fight across the galaxy to defeat the evil Wolf Empire, challenge other players in online battles, promote a roster of unique heroes, build bases with strong defenses and climb the ranks to reach a new planet every week!

Do you have what it takes, Commander?

FEATURES
Play with millions of other players, raid thousands of enemy Bases
Reach new planets filled with exclusive content every 7 days
Combine countless Spells to plan unique battle strategies
Build your Spaceship and upgrade your Base against attacks
Fight the evil Wolf Empire in the 100-mission Story Campaign
Get challenged by 72 whacky Operations with funky designs
Earn crates to unlock Troopers, collect cards to promote them
Available in English, French, German, Spanish and Portuguese!

Note: this game requires an internet connection.

VIP Member Subscription Info:
• 1 month
• $9.99 USD per month
• Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase
• Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end
of the current period
• Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and
identify the cost of the renewal
• Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the
user’s Account Settings after purchase
• No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during active subscription period

Loot Boxes:
• All-Star Troopers features loot boxes
• Amounts displayed in loot boxes pop-up indicate actual reward (no odds)
• For in-game currency intervals, odds are linear (computer generated number within interval)

Like All-Star Troopers on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/AllStarTroopers

title: Crime Mafia Gangsters Battle Royale
description:
Welcome to Mafia Worldf!  Roll up on a dangerous new trip through the city in San Andreas Fault in Battle Royale today!

Pickup different items from the environment for your survival,Attacks ordinary citizens, kills policemen, steals different kinds of vehicles. You are provided the unique opportunity to become a super villain. 
Many different Ammunition and Weapons are at your disposal. Become a chief on the streets of criminality in San Andreas !
Now you’re the most wanted man in this dog-eat-dog city where crime is everywhere. 

Welcome to San Andreas,where fortunes are made and lives are lost with a roll of the dice!
For fans of FPS action, Auto Racing, driving (autos or tanks),games with car theft, and free mobile games.

The greatest criminal of all the times. Untouchable theft with a reputation of saucy fellow. You are a number one wanted person among all the cops in the city.
Participate in crazy chases around the town. Be fast and fierce. Don’t hesitate and don’t spare your foes.

Purchase vest weaponry in the city shop. Get yourself best cars. Level up and rise your proficiency with everything you can buy.
Rush into the criminal city that never sleeps.

Discover missions, vehicles, characters, weapons, locations, and much, much more for each game.
No other app offers this amount of accurate insights, tips and game information with useful companion-play features.


Features:

- More than 100 types of transport
- A huge open world
- Beautiful graphics & Realistic physics
- Multiple weapons & kits in stores
- Customize your characters

Missions:

- Grand Endless space for police actions: hit and run, auto stealing, police firefight and 
    even more
- Well detailed graphic from real cars and places
- Third person gameplay: car stealing, man shooting and driving are all for you, with the 
   most powerful 3D engine
- Shopping and styling. Choose your outfit from more that ten modern catalogs
- Real-time level-ups and talent improvements

title: Strike Combat Pixel Online
description:
Looking for a S.W.A.T. vs Terrorists game? Strike Combat Pixel Online is a mixed both cs feel and crafting game
Play a fascinating dynamic first-person shooter Pixel with friends and other players online around the world . 
** Modes ** 
Game has more than 3 different game modes from which you can select: 
- Team Deathmatch 
- Deathmatch (Player vs all)
- Normal
** Maps ** 
More than 20 different maps, in which every day there are dynamic battles.
From small maps to a small group of friends, to large maps on which you have to work hard to win.

More than 20 types of weapons like pistols, machine guns, shotguns, machine guns, rifles and melee weapons.

title: Mafia Crime City Fighter - Gangster Survival Game
description:
The commando shooter is back in town for the vegas gangster survival of this beautiful city. Grand city is piled up with mafia gangster survival and criminal escape prisoners. The armed forces have taken over the area to raise mafia crime city fight. Survival rescue against the dangerous mafia gangster vegas and legend warriors of underworld. Criminal Russian mafia cartel are dangerous terrorist escaped from hard time prisoners. As an elite fighter of commando your duty is to rescue innocent citizens of grand city. Payback these mafia crime city Russian gangster crime against the most wanted criminals.


You have been assigned a high level secret mission. This involves sniper shooting and assassination of terrorist mafia group. Rescue citizens and fellow agents captured by captured by underworld russian mafia cartel. As professional trained fighter and spy, execute dangerous operations inside the grand city. Perform hero survival missions. Take down terrorist enemy sniper and armed gangsters with assault shooting. Spy and assassinate and play key role to serve your country like a real hero fighter. Sneak inside the gangland as spy agent. 


You are a top rated high level trained secret mafia crime city fighter and survival hero. Just get started using your elite sneaky skills to win the war against mafia shooting gangster vegas. Enjoy one of the best survival criminal crime city game. Complete various tasks and engage extreme crime city fight. Perform operation for survival of grand city against evil mafia survival criminals. Use deadly arms and weapons. Create panic and chaos inside russian mafia cartel gangs. 


Become hero and face the mafia crime city mafia armed forces, let them know you are a true army commando hero survival mission. Climb the rooftop and mark Russian mafia cartel thugs. Survive the city battlefield and complete FPS survival fighter games mission. Deploy the critical squad force shooting hero mission and assassin mafia rival fight. The Russian terrorists occupied the grand city. Accept the mission of the army warrior blood. Destroy terrorists, attack enemy base around the grand mafia crime city. 


Trained at the US army school you have to show your professional fighter skills. Eliminate super-villains in this ultimate Mafia Crime City Fighter-Gangster Survival Criminal. The greedy Russian mafia cartel and Godfather has given a brawl against his most dangerous line-up of mafia crime master villains.


Mafia Crime City Fighter Gangster Survival Criminal 3D Features:
✔️ Amazing 3D City Environment.

✔️ Climb, Walk, Run and Fly in Vegas gangster survival

title: Vice Spider Rope Hero
description:
Looking for Amazing Spider Super Hero Human Game? Then download Vice Spider Rope Hero.  He can fly, climb walls and with his super power he can save people in the city.

Use all your fantastic power and marvelous strategy to protect the people of San Andreas. This is the best vice spider superhero games available on store. 

It's time to show everyone who’s boss by using your supernatural powers and shooting rivals with web and ruling the streets. You are not policeman. You are a Superhero, who don't need for glory - you have a greed for revenge. 

Are you ready to rescue a people from horrible life among blood, shots, bandits and killers? The style of city is similar to Miami or Las Vegas but actualy it's New York. Become a chief on the streets of anti criminality in town. 

Dominate the city with a devastating firepower of advanced military vehicles or upgrade your hero to knock down enemies in a few kicks!

To stop these criminals you have to complete a lot of missions and you need to learn how to fly fast and reach the people in danger. When you are driving around in San Andreas you can look on the minimap for missions or you can use the quick buttons to start right away a mission. Download the game for free.

Features:

★ Superhero Game 
★ Fly as super hero
★ Epic storyline
★ Widescreen resolution support
★ Beautiful new graphics

MISSIONS
-> Girl is in danger. She is stuck on a tall building. Rescue her before it’s too late.

-> Girl is stuck on a malfunctioned ferris wheel of San Andreas. Rescue her.

-> Shipping boat is on fire. Save people on them before the ship sinks. 

-> Save a man stuck on a tower.

-> Hiking tragedy : Save people on the mountains.

title: Ball Helix Jump Helix - Spring Ball Jumping Down
description:
Ball Helix Jump Helix - Spring Ball Jumping - is a twist jump leaping ball game. In which you have to control falling balls. In ball jump games, ball takes jump in helical spring and you have to get the ball jump down but avoiding tower fall.

One-tap easy-to-learn controls, rich visual effects and addictive gameplay mechanics.
An exciting adventure of the bouncing ball through the helix tower labyrinth...

Ball Helix Jump Helix - Spring Ball Jumping Down with crazy ball jump and very addictive gameplay. Jump and complete hexil maze and levels. Earn gems to unlock more stunning jumping balls including football, baseball, tennis ball, cricket ball, plastic ball, color ball, and many more.

Keep your helix game run by keeping jumpy ball in control. As you drop ball, the game will end with your ball dropping and the helix show of ball jumping games will end. Now, you have to jump and jump down on heliex to be a helx jumper master.

You can move the spiral ball left and right with moving your finger as hopping ball on screen. Keep your eyes on hopping ball, because in spring jump, ball jumps very quickly and the ball falls down and jumps down and down freely.

So, keep enjoy the spring ball and drop ball game but don't be a ball dropper. Keep the helix ball jumpy and avoid it to be a falling ball. As you know ball games are very popular now a days and specially color switching and coloring tower is the best one. In which you have to do tower jumping and helix jumping.

How to Play:
Simple controls just slide the fingers right and left for the helix rotation and jump of the ball. Try to avoid the odd color spots helix and let the ball pass down through the bottom.

title: Pixel Zombies: Endless Shooting War
description:
Now experience the world war Z with the Pixel Zombies: Endless Shooting game. This evil game is full of monstrous zombies and dangerous species. Pixel zombies are eating wild animals and innocent humans alive just to fulfill their hunger.
So, grab a zombie gun and have war with the different zombie species. Because the Zombie fighting city is full of pixelated zombies and evil monsters. Participate in pixel zombie battles and zombie tournaments. Become a crack shot gun dam shooter and hunt down the human-eating zombies.
Play this dead city zombie shooter game to save the grand city and the whole world. There are pixel villages, pixel cities, and pixel characters in this zombie shooting game. Complete the levels to earn coins and buy the advanced pixel guns for ultimate shooting.
Explore the zombie world and shoot them down in the research labs and confined research centers. There are zombie nurses, zombie humans, and zombie dogs. There is an open world pixel map for your guidance and the location of evil zombies.
Become a deadly zombie shooter who has to hunt down the zombie nurses and zombie humans for his ultimate survival. The zombies also spit the virus from their mouths. The virus is a green fluid which makes you crazy and eventually creates you a walking zombie and living dead.
Play the fps zombie game mode to collect special rewards and achieve a higher score. Sweep zombies from the zombie world city and the entire world. Defeat the Zombies coming to eat you alive. Strive, survive, and thrive in the zombie evil city. Save the kids, persons, animals, and birds from the zombie traps.

description:
Helix Jump: Spiral Tile Drop Game is super simple to learn yet insanely addictive to play. Experiencing adventure of the bouncing ball through the helix tower labyrinth.

What is Helix Jump: Spiral Tile Drop Game?
Helix Jump: Spiral Tile Drop Game is an endless play style of game where you try to get a ball down a set of tiles as you avoid red tiles that end your turn. It is simple, but pretty addictive.

* Rotate the helix maze by sliding your finger horizontally across your screen to guide the jumping ball through the gaps in the helix tower.

title: Frontline Survival Terror Critical Strike
description:
Title: Frontline Survival Critical Terror Strike

Step in the battleground to defeat the enemies with the powerful armory.  

Experience the action-packed combat in the world of shooting battleground. You have to be the savior hero in this special ops of modern fps war. The interactive & stylish 3D environment will keep involved in the gameplay. Let’s get ready to defeat the enemies counter assault with your amazing handguns. Concentrate & spot the rivals position to quickly eliminate before they take over the arena. You’ll have to follow the survival rules to win & lead the battle royale.  In this intense warfare improve your skills & abilities of shooting. So be ready to play the unique & addictive fps game in the realistic immersive battle arena.

How to Play :
Soldier you just have to select your shooting gun, move your aim pointer to red circle to auto-fire the shooter enemy. Be quick in reloading your gun to defend from damage. You have to sustain your health & be careful not to shoot the hostages. Collect all the rewards to upgrade your weapons. In this fun & addictive gameplay become a hero of the battleground.

Features: 
•    First Person Shooter 
•    Amazing graphics with awesome animation
•    Easy & smooth controls to use
•    Various handguns available
•    Autofire: just place your pointer accurately
•    Astounding sound effects

title: Mini Beasts Battlelands Combat
description:
Fight for survival in an epic last man standing single player third person Mini Beasts Battlelands Combat - but not as you know it
Made for mobile, Battlelands kombat is a casual gun game for everyone to enjoy. Dominate the arena in Solo or join forces with fellow battlers in Duos. Choose your spot, loot weapons and armor and get ready for the fight of your life! Battle it out on a huge map with awesome locations like the NY city, US  and LA. Or maybe you’ll hide away in Camper’s Paradise? Whatever your strategy, don’t get caught by the storm! With a variety of guns and players you can perfect your shooting skills and become the best battler in town. Will you choose the sniper, shotgun, rifle or pistol? Remember to race to supply drops to compete for the special minigun and bazooka! Super simple controls, a fun and quirky art style and pick-up-and-play gameplay make Battlelands combat the best free game on mobile that you won’t want to put down. 

Fight in the arena with your favorite hero and become the best player of the Ultimate Show!
beasts battle Ultimate Show is the definitive mobile device offline action game! Choose one of the mighty heroes and fight against enemy, be it solo or in a team, it’s up to you! There are many ways to become a legend of the game arena.

AN AMAZING Beasts Battlelands Combat EXPERIENCE

1vs5 matches? 1v10 fights? No, this is the Ultimate Show, where only the strong survive. Enter the Ultimate Show, defeat all your enemies, and become master of the single player arena. Enjoy the action of offline combat against other players from around the map of Ultimate Warrior. stickman gangs decided to sort out among themselves and find out which gang is steeper than the rest of the gangs. Stickman decided to make funny and ridiculous beast combative wrestling fights. Become a participant in funny fights without rules. Be ready for anything. Be smart and be cunning to help your gang win. Fight like an beast, use the environment to wrap the situation in your favor.

Drop the beasts - stickmans from the precipices, throw them into the water, do not give them a chance to win. And do not forget about the fun. After all, combating wrestling shooting stickman of beasts is cheerful and ridiculous. Ridiculous ragdoll physics will surely amuse you and your friends. Go through all the levels, fight at different locations and help your gang of Stickmans win. Become a wrestling champion in the game Mini Beasts Battlelands Combat game.

title: Ngự Long 3D
descriptionHTML:
PK Hay Lấy Cả Thiên Hạ
Ngự Long 3D là một tựa game nhập vai quốc chiến có mật độ PK liên tục và dày đặc, phù hợp cho bất kỳ ai đam mê sự cuồng nhiệt trên các chiến trường. Ở phiên bản hiện tại trò chơi mang tới 3 phái gồm Bá Đao (đao), Ma Thương (thương) và Vũ Cơ (quạt). Mỗi phái đều có tạo hình và bộ kỹ năng riêng biệt. Đặc biệt 3 phái này còn có thể tự do chuyển đổi qua lại.
Về PK, Ngự Long 3D đảm bảo bất kỳ ai tham gia cũng sẽ được sống trong một chiến trường khổng lồ, khi hai phe Chính Tà đánh nhau liên tục ngày đêm. Tại đây người chơi còn có thể tận hưởng lại cảm giác mà dường như đã mất từ lâu như chặn cổng PK, khi phe Chính có thể đứng chặn cổng thành của phe Tà và ngược lại. Thứ hai, đó là PK và KS boss, khi người chơi có thể tiêu diệt một người chơi khác để chiếm lấy con boss cho riêng mình. Chỉ nghe tới đó mà nhiều game thủ đã rất nóng lòng muốn tận tay trải nghiệm siêu phẩm MMORPG này rồi.
Nếu, bạn là người thích trải nghiệm chiến trường PK và các hoạt động PVP trong game;
Nếu, bạn muốn tận hưởng cảm giác làm vua, đứng đầu thiên hạ và điều khiển một quốc gia;
Nếu, bạn chán nản với việc phải đánh quái săn kinh nghiệm ngày qua ngày và không có mục tiêu;
Nếu bạn yêu thích sự trải nghiệm như đổi phái chuyển phe chỉ với vài thao tác;
Thì,…
Ngự Long 3D là tựa game MMORPG thích hợp nhất dành cho bạn.
Người chơi không còn chịu cảnh cày cuốc nhàm chán, mệt mỏi mà thay vào đó là tận hưởng sự nhiệt huyết, cảm giác hừng hực khí thế trên các chiến trường đa dạng từ cảnh sắc đến quy mô.
summary: Ngự Long 3D - PK Hay Lấy Cả Thiên Hạ

title: Superhero Lara- The Tomb Fighter
description:
Become the Best Tomb Fighter with Superhero Lara in ancient tombs and old temples. Fight with super monsters and evil villains by becoming an ancient relic hero raider. Play the action survival game to complete tomb missions and temple findings. Enjoy the exciting features of this superhero fighting game. Become an elite commando fighter with superhero Lara in fighting battle rings. Play this freestyle action fighting game and enjoy the amazing environments like the jungle forest, snowy mountains, and sandy desert.
Fight with the epic monsters and evil guys in the superhero battles. Experience the ultimate Lara fighting and endless crafting. Defeat your super enemies and win the relic artifacts as a reward. Become an elite Lara agent and also shoot at your enemies while fighting them in a tournament battle. 
	Superhero Lara- The Tomb Fighter Features:
	2018 Tomb Fighter Raider
	Collect Relics, Collect Artifacts, Collect Dark Objects
	Relic Demon Monsters
	Stealth Action Fighting Game
	Superhero Lara
	Fighting Battles, Fighting Rings
	Amazing Challenges, Epic Tournaments
	Ancient Style Tomb Fighting
	Temples full of Artifacts and Dark Objects
	Dynamic Adventure Fighting
	Find the Lost Temples
Play this army fighting game and enjoy the tomb battles and temple tournaments. You are a temple croft raider who has to find the relics in the ancient historical places and well known buried temples. Play this new action fighting game to have a fight with scary demon monsters, super villains, and dangerous enemies. Have epic fighting battles in the ancient tombs and collect special relics to upgrade your skills. Some relics also give you the special superpowers like throwing fireballs, hiding, super strength, and ultimate power.
Download this action-fight game now to enjoy the ancient temple battles and endless tomb fighting. Defeat the character in your front to get special rewards and snatch the relics from a tomb running raider. Become the superhero Lara and search the jungles, mountains, caves, tunnels, and water to find the dark objects, relics, and special artifacts.

title: Kari Slodier: Classic Commando
description:
Kari Slodier: Classic Commando  is a vertically scrolling, run & gun shoot 'em up arcade game.

The player takes the role of commando-like warriors named Ralf and Clark, who must try to reach the village of Ikari. Enemy units attempting to kill the player include tanks, enemy soldiers and helicopters. A number of power-ups along the way help the player achieve victory.

Kari Slodier was the first popular video game to use rotary joysticks: those which could be rotated in addition to being pushed in eight directions.  The game also featured two buttons, one for the standard gun and another for lobbing grenades. It allowed two players to play cooperatively, side-by-side — one of the few games to do so at the time — and to use vehicles. 

The player begins as one of two commando-type warriors, garbed in red (Ralf) or blue (Clark). They must proceed from the bottom of the screen upwards, towards the village of Kari. Trying to prevent them from reaching the village are enemy soldiers and other units. Along the way, players may commandeer enemy tanks and helicopters to help fight their way through the enemy personnel. The tanks are immune to enemy bullets, but have a limited supply of fuel and will sustain damage when it runs out or the tank is caught in an explosion, taking the player with it unless he can exit the tank and get clear before it blows up. The helicopters have two different weapons, a spread gun and a cannon, and may fly over water.

Kari Slodier was the first Commando style game to give the player a limited amount of ammunition. Turning the joystick changes the direction the character faced independent of the direction the character was moving, as controlled by pushing the joystick. This gave the player freedom to attack or walk in eight different directions. No shot is fired from directly in front of the player; the warrior uses the machine gun in his right hand, and throws grenades with his left. If a player character takes too long moving up screen, the computer starts using "call for fire". A red spot appears below him; this is tracking fire to speed up the game.

title: Real Gunship Battle Helicopter War 3D
description:
It's not a game of rescue aeroplanes, you don't have any ally, you might cross the Apache, Atlantis, even the brim of the world, and you've been flying like a hawk to combat against targets. This is not a ForeFlight Mobile of airlift supplies developed by ARI, in this game you gotta be like the hero Rambo to throw missiles. It does’t need to fare the game either, all you have to do is pick up arms, drive a battleship in the oxygen-thin sky, and act as a major to punch enemies.
In this game there are more than 100 missions to achieve.
If you complete the mission in time, you can purchase mission props and open up the next level. To start the mission you need to start up warship first from the home base and fly towards the enemy strike area . When your aircraft enters the death zone of your strike area first mission is to aim then plan to strike the targeted point and protect yourself from their fire and rocket launcher.
The enemy is very strong but you are well trained chopper striker. You have entered in the mid field of desert of the death war and you need to recon and targ et their diploid area camps, ships, tanks and other equipment. Your bombers are loaded with full of ammo and worlds best modern equipment. So just show your skills and it's as easy to defeat an enemy as it is to defeat a homeless canter, and then hijack what you deserve. But to tell you, there’ll be no coppers who maybe ride on Halley with a bell here to arrest you when you are going to landing. There are different levels with different missions and different environmental area like desert mountain and deep sea. The sound quality is stunning, you will hear a real sound of strike with thrill and terror. The game makes you feel joyable in battle after battle, and the big bangs seem to bring you back to 1942. We have introduced 3D graphics for this game.
Real Gunship Battle Helicopter War 3D Features:
- Different types of helicopters
- Heavy equipment and ammunition.	
- Real scenery and 3D graphics.
- Real sound effect of firing.
- More than 100 missions to achieve.

Have fun in a new innovative 3D animal sniper hunting with real helicopter simulation game with awesome game play environment. Hunt multiple different animals with sniper rifle from helicopter to complete the objectives.

Take control of your heli to fly around and move quickly in the sanctuary and protect animals.

description:
Zombie shooter is the one of the best zombie shooting game on this store. Zombie shooter is a new and exciting chapter of adventure for your survival against zombies. It has been months since the dangerous virus has been released in the world. No one is safe and zombies has spread everywhere. Survival is very difficult in a world full zombies. Get ready to protect your town from these zombies attack. Take your sniper gun and shoot zombies in the head and save humanity in this FPS zombie survival shooting game. Select your favorite sniper gun, fire weapons and aim zombies and kill zombies as a professional sniper shooter. You are the only professional sniper shooter left in the town so get ready to show some skills and save your people from zombies. 
The undead zombies has turn the world into doomsday. There is no one left for you to trust. The only thing that save your town from these zombies attacks are your sniper guns. Help survivors by killing zombies and stop the end of the world. Travel to different areas in your town and take your sniper guns with you. Take aim at zombies and strategically fire using sniper shooting skills. Keep your fingers on the trigger and shoot every zombie that come near to you.
Become the ultimate zombie killer and stop the virus of zombie infection in zombie shooter: survival game. You are the only professional sniper shooter and it is your responsibility to save humanity from zombie attacks. Kill all zombies with your sniper gun before they hunt you down. You must be quick in this shooting game. Zombie shooter has different mission to clear. Each mission have different difficulties and number of zombies. Use your sniper gun and kill everyone that is coming in your way.
zombie shooter: survival game has impressive game graphics that zombie are more real then ever. It has the best visual effects for the best zombie shooting actions.  
Features of zombie shooter: survival game:
3D game graphics with detailed scenes and objectives. 
Challenging missions. 
Advanced weapons. 
Optimized and smooth game controls. 
High quality sound effects. 
3D game environment.
Test your survival skills.

title: Sniper Gun FPS Shooter King 2018
description:
Welcome to the Sniper Gun FPS Shooter King 2018 best shooting game that pits you in battle of Zombie VS FPS shooter modes and hundreds of missions.

Become a legend of shooting games and take your sniper gun in your hand for taking revenge from zombies. Announce the sniper strike in city like real gangster and hunt the zombie robots in best FPS game 2018. Sharp your archers skills to catch zombie and earn the gold in sniper shooting king master battle. Some soul of zombies attack on your city to spread the virus and to increase the crime rate but you are the last hope for the citizen in this ultra shooting game so become super shooter in this free shooting game to catch zombies dead or alive like real commando. Step into knight survival shooting mission and clean the zombie virus from city with help of your best FPS skills to become king of 2018 shooting game. Now what are you waiting for download this Sniper Gun FPS Shooter King 2018 game and start to catch the zombies.

Features Of 3D Sniper Game 2018

-Realistic 3D shooting battlefield environment
-Top-notch sound effects
- Radar vision positioning the enemy's position
- Immersive action filled missions
- Play anytime, anywhere (offline gaming enabled)
- Realistic combat mechanics
- Tons of letal guns and mortal weapons
- Addicting FPS gameplay
- Easy and intuitive controls
- Encounter the zombies with your best sniper shooting skills


Forget all other shooting games. Here, your duty will include racing against time like frontier, exploding helicopters, killing zombies and quite a few shots in slow motion. Survival is necessary! But can you solve the puzzle, save the victims and kill only the right target hidden in the crowd? Can you stop the unknown virus from spreading? TRY it best of luck!

title: Car Theft Mafia Game
description:
Car Theft Mafia Game There is a whole black market around cars and for this to exist there must be people who are dedicated to car theft. You must become a thief of high-end vehicles and get money for each of the robberies. You must do it very carefully as there are strong security measures that you will have to dodge to get to each of the cars and finish the robbery successfully.


\ \ Game history / /
At first, James does not have cash because he is new to the city of Miami. Help James beat all public enemies and collect gold coins and cash in the crime city. You need to follow and complete the history of the game and the missions.
You should also be aware of the police cars on the road, avoid them and keep collecting coins and cash. Also to avoid obstacles like other cars, gangsters, mafias on the way to earn more high score.

Car Theft Mafia Action Game In this complete action pack of realistic mobster and mafia game, you need to control your player James Adams and explore the city in San Andres. Car Theft Mafia Game is not just another crime simulator game from Miami, Gangster Mafia Cool City Action Game In this action pack complete realistic gangster and mafia game.

\\ Feauters //
# Cool visual effects and nice graphics.
# Different system missions, find and complete all of them.
# Fantastic selection of weapons.


Car Theft Mafia Game is now available to play for free on Android! And soon it will be available for all mobile platforms

Play with your hero, take an powerful weapons and throows knifs, make everything die.

Feature :
- Battlegrounds with tons of enemies everywhere
- Several types of tap ennemies with different abilities, adapted to the different targets of the mission

title: Infinity Battle
description:
This is a survival game against a very powerful villain.

About Game:-

Tanos is the evil king of this universe.He has somehow conquered all the infinity stones by trick and has become very powerful.You are required to survive against him as long as possible.Beware of his magical spells due to which stones and meteors may cause you damage.Score points by hitting Tanos.Each hits will fetch you 5 points.Pick up med kits to revive your health.Choose your hero to save the universe.

You will be provided with the following two heroes.

About Heroes:-

Hulkman - Following the accidental exposure to gamma rays during the detonation of an experimental bomb,a young scientist Dr.Ghosh is physically transformed into Hulkman when subjected to emotional stress, at or against his will, often leading to rampages and tremendous strength which is proportionate to his level of anger.

Iron-Hero - A wealthy Indian business man and technician, Jony Banerjee develops a powered suit of armour by adding weapons and other technological devices.He uses the suit to protect the world as Iron-Hero.


Choose any one of the above heroes to survive against Tanos.

Users can also share their net score on social media.

All the best

title: Perfect Swish – Addictive Basketball Swish Game
description:
Do you like taking on the hardest games ever to constantly push your skills to the edge? If your answer is yes, then Perfect Swish – Addictive Basketball Swish is just the perfect game for you right now!

This new arcade game is amazingly designed with an awesome environment to give you the best experience while playing it. As a player, your task is to concentrate and maintain your focus so that you can collect all falling basketballs without letting any one of them fall outside the rim. But, keep in mind that your mission will not be that easy because the game will get faster and more difficult so you should be fast and precise to move the rim and collect as many basketballs as you can to score the highest possible score. Don't forget that the game will ends if you let any ball go without making a swish. 
Perfect Swish is a cool and insanely addictive throwing game to tickle your brain. Get hours of fun by playing this awesome swish game, you will fall in love with it, the moment you start playing it. Our arcade game offers hours of fun that are free of any charge. Addictive gameplay to keep you hooked for hours with awesome fun and frolic. 

★★ Why do you need to download and install Perfect Swish on your Android smartphone or tablet for Free instead of other brain challenging or brain teasing games? ★★
✓ Simple, attractive and high-quality graphics designed especially for this throwing game. You will have an awesome feeling while playing in this amazing environment. 
✓ Very easy to play! All that you have to do is to collect as many basketballs as you can. Very easy!

title: Spiky Storm
description:
Life is not a bed of roses it's full of spike & storm. 
As our life, the goal of the game is fight against the spikes as long as you alive.

Instructions
♦  Tap anywhere to shoot.
♦  Tilt your device to control the plane.
♦  Avoid collision between plane & spikes.
♦  Score will increase for collide with positive numbers.
♦  Score will decrease for collide with negative numbers.

title: Pixel Invaders
description:
Dodge, shoot and fly your way through the galaxy in Pixel Invaders, an endless space shooter designed to give you the feel of an 80s arcade game in an exciting, modern mobile gaming experience. With beautiful graphics, immersive sounds and addictive gameplay, Pixel Invaders will turn a 20-minute lunch break into a 2-hour gaming marathon!

CLASSIC ARCADE FEEL
"Pixel Invaders has made me feel like a kid again. I Absoluely love it!"

With carefully designed 16-bit graphics, specially tailored sound effects and arcade-style music, Pixel Invaders will transport you back to the 80s while giving you the full experience of a modern mobile game.

ENDLESS GAMEPLAY
With multiple different enemy types, exciting power-ups and a rich upgrade system, you will never get bored of playing Pixel Invaders! 

FREE DAILY REWARDS AND ACHIEVEMENTS SYSTEM
50 coins off an upgrade? We've got you covered with free daily rewards to help you beat your high score. Strive to acquire all of the achievements in the game for an extra challenge!

MULTIPLE ENEMY TYPES
No two games of Pixel Invaders will be the same, with multiple enemy types, and several powerups to spice up your gameplay experience.

If you have any issues please e-mail us at ka_mobilegames@outlook.com and we will be sure to get back in touch with you!

title: Brawling Animals
description:
Welcome to the Jungle! Release your inner beast and jump into epic, action-packed multiplayer battles! 
 
BATTLE IN EXCITING GAME MODES
Engage in a fun and chaotic arenas where players battle to dominance, may the best brawler win!
 
COLLECT AND UPGRADE ANIMALS
Unlock a variety of characters with epic abilities, upgrade them with special tokens to further unleash their power.
 
BECOME THE KING OF THE JUNGLE
Climb the local and global leaderboards to prove your strength and skill among the brawlers!

Features:
- A fast-paced multiplayer battle royale
- Battles against players from all over the world.
- Unlock new, powerful Animals - each with a different playstyle and abilities.
- Climb to the top of the leaderboards in global and local rankings.
- Upgrade your favorite Animal for that critical edge.

title: Monster Battle City Survival Mania
description:
Epic Monster Battle City Survival Mania is ready for action game lover where you become city monster and fight with dangerous gangster. You can drive your car and chase criminals to stop them. Enjoy two different environment like City as well as Jungle. Fight with animals like angry gorilla and wild lion to save civilians from these jungle beasts. 
Enjoy two story mode game like Forest and Grand city. In City mode you play as city monster and save civilians from gangsters as well as corrupt police officers. Fight with criminals with the help of fighting skills like ground punch attach and strong kick attack. Destroy helicopter with the help of jump attack and beat your rivals by playing Monster Battle City Survival Mania.

In Jungle mode you enter in dark jungle to save civilians from wild animals. Fight with Wild lions as well as Mad Gorilla with the help ground punch attack. Thrilling missions are ready to blast the game in gaming world and monster game lovers. City gangster are trying to snatch money from innocent civilians with the help of evil forces. It’s your duty to save the civilians from these bad guys and survive in the city as well as dark forest.  
You will love this monster strike game and monster battle league in grand city with your powerful attack in battle field. Destroy enemies’ cars as well as helicopters with the help of mega jump attack and ground punch attack by playing monster squad city battle mania. Beat your enemy to earn points and unlock new monster as well as next exciting levels.  You are city monster savior everyone is depending on you and it’s your duty to save civilians from bad guys as well as corrupt officers. Bad forces are trying to convert lovely city and jungle in to graveyard with their evil forces.

Key Features:
•	Become Incredible Monster City Savior 
•	Choose your favorite Story Mode as well as Monster 
•	Drive car to chase bad guys
•	Fight with animals and save civilians
•	Use your Jump attack and ground punch attack to survive

Enemy loft Strike combines immersive 3D environments with intense FPS gameplay. 

In this extreme action & adventure bravo combat, You have to attack different enemy bases and islands which are taken by the deadly enemies. Grab your gun and prepare for epic warfare and furious FPS action! Show no mercy to the alien army, and take back your planet! You will also have a training mission where you must prepare yourself for the advance weapons and army combat techniques. You are expected to take the enemy bases on your own and survive their onslaught. You must find and use the modern  weapons, food and health within these bases and islands. title: Bumper Cars Crash Drive
description:
Bumper car games never have been this much fun. In this Bumper Cars Crash Drive game you will have the chance to ride in many different bumper cars and beat all of the opponents in the special car crash arena we have made for you! The challenge for you will be to master the extreme bumper car machine in order to destroy all the vehicles & bumping cars that are there in the destruction arena in the minimum amount of time, in order to be crowned as the national bumper car destruction champion. You will have to eliminate all bumper car rivals before anyone of them crosses the finish line. But always remember, it’s not important that you win, but that you have fun in this amazing bumper car games. 

All you have to do is crash drive & hit your opponent hard with your steering wheel every time opponent tries to come near you and try to crash your bumper car. In this epic game you have to improve yourself with each level and the car driving challenges you with rival bumping cars leading to a Cup. You will have to carry out amazing bumper car crash collision stunts with steering wheel and defeat all rival electric cars in epic bumper car crash course. On the racing tracks, excavations are set everywhere and time clock is ticking down. So, you have to hurry up before the time meter counts down to zero. If you land on a mine, the life of your bumper cars will reduce. 

In the challenge arena you have to smash all of your rival bumping cars before the time runs out or before they cross the finish line. Now this style of bumper car simulator is rather difficult than the other bumper cars styles. In this car crash arena you dash from the start line and try to knock down every single one of your opponent and destroy their car which will get them eliminated. You will have to eliminate all bumper car rivals before anyone of them crosses the finish line. Consider this as bumper car training. So what are you waiting for Download this Bumper Cars Crash Drive & get ready to knock players off the stage with your bumper.

🏎️ A lot of different bumper car missions for you to play and enjoy!

title: Fire Fighter Truck Robot:Real Robot Rescue Truck
description:
Game Play Station(GPS) Studio Team Present “Fire Fighter Truck Robot:Real Robot Rescue Truck” Game this Grand Robot Super Truck is basically flying truck or Fire fighter truck Used for firefighting operations.In this  Real Robot Firefighter truck:Robot Super Truck game your task is to extinguish the fire and do robot wars against super robot.You can perform robot transformation by clicking the change mode button,you can perform flying truck robot transformation and enjoy the flying truck and perform yours rescue mission easily and early as compare to other superhero robot and super robots.

This  Fire Fighter Truck Robot:Real Robot Rescue Truck  game is totally concept base on fire engine So First of all what is Fire engine .A fire engine also known as a fire apparatus, fire truck, or fire appliance is a vehicle designed primarily for firefighting operations . The terms "fire engine" and "fire truck" are often used interchangeably.But we GPS Studio is offering new concept of fire engine Robot. 

Features of Fire Fighter Truck Robot:Real Robot Rescue Truck  :

•	Robot transformation animation into car and car transformation animation into Robot.
•	Flying Fire truck option by clicking on the fly mode.
•	Smooth and easy controls of fire truck or fire fighter truck.
•	Different rescue missions Like Fire Extinguish ,Fight with super robots enemies and 
        Super robo cars enemies.
•	Firefighter Missile option to destroy the Super robo car.
•	Hand to hand combat with super futuristic robots.
•	Different Fire Fighter truck model that can perform robot transformation animation.


Game Play of Fire Fighter Truck Robot:Real Robot Rescue Truck  :

The Game play of this Real Robot Firefighter truck:Robot Super Truck game is very interesting and charming ,not boring like other flying truck robot wars. In Real Robot Firefighter truck:Robot Super Truck Game you as a firefighter robot firetruck will strategically move through prominent locations and fire rescue or fire truck rescue innocent people of big city from different damaged buildings. Be a american firefighter or fire brigade simulator along with advanced rescue mission simulator and perform fireman fire fighter duty in each rescue mission of survival city. Are you fan of robot fighting game along with highly engaging robot transforming games, then this game will fulfill your requirements. In this robot battle game, you will robot wars battle against vicious superhero robot or super robot.In this muscle car super robot truck game ,you can drive the firefighter truck ,fly the truck ,transform into robot by robot transformation and can robot wars with futuristic robots. In this robot transformation game, you will battle in different city rescue missions as fire brigade or fight with futuristic robot for quick fire rescue or pro fire truck rescue of innocent people of grand city. Be quick as other super robot  or superhero robot will face time constraint in reaching the rescue spot, you will have Flying power and transformation power so use these power to finish the rescue mission and kill the robots in robot wars.

In this  Fire Fighter Truck Robot:Real Robot Rescue Truck  Game you have also a chance to fight with Grand car Robots,transform your super robot into the super car and destroy the enemy robot car.
